originalText.text: We have absolutely loved working with Jeanette and her entire team! Our condo remodel is taking place in two different phases and after having the first phase complete, we cannot wait to continue to work with Jeanette! She is the ultimate professional, and makes a difficult process seem easy! There isn’t any problem that she cannot fix! Her ability to get the project done on time is amazing. Most important is her impeccable taste and having the ability to read her client and focus in on style and comfort that works well with her designs.  I have and will continue to use and recommend Jeanette as she is as close to perfection in the design industry!

originalText.text: We worked with Hubley Design to renovate our home in Florida. Jeanette is a fabulous designer who has changed our home from old style Mediterranean to modern Palm Beach. Jeanette has an eye for style.. She and her team were fabulous to work with. She is responsive and cost effective. Thanks again Jeanette for making our home so awesome...

originalText.text:
We are about to embark on another project with Hubley Design.
Jeanette and her Staff are wonderful to work with.  They are professional and detail oriented.  Their commitment to our project was immeasurable, and their creativity, energy, and sophisticated taste has helped turn around our tired condo into a beautiful home.  Jeanette is warm, engaging, and takes much pride in her work.  We are thankful for her help.

originalText.text:
The day we signed Jeanette Hubley-Lasher to renovate and decorate our “New” 25 year old Florida home turned out to be an auspicious one. Our daunting project morphed into an exciting yet manageable affair in no time. The confidence we have in Jeanette and her staff is now a given.
Warm, efficient, contemporary, knowledgeable, honest and painstaking diligent and more…all uniquely apply We might add that the unanticipated friendship that remains is a huge bonus.
Without qualification we recommend Jeanette and her professional company to anyone who is looking for the very best.

Sent from my iPhone

originalText.text: I have worked with Jeanette and her team on several projects over the past  decade. She has helped to transform my apartment into an elegant yet tranquil home. Her taste is exceptional and her suggestions for each room have been imaginative . I have learned so much from Jeanette about color, fabric and design. I value her insights and suggestions ! I highly recommend Jeanette!
